ENTRY            G3148   20251217   20260508   20260508       G059
SUBENT        G3148001   20251217   20260508   20260508       G059
BIB                 12         23
TITLE      Isomeric yield ratio of 115m,gCd in the 116Cd(g,n) and
           116Cd(n,2n) reactions
AUTHOR     (H.Naik, G.N.Kim, W.Y.Jang, T.H.Nguyen)
INSTITUTE  (3INDTRM,3KORKNU)
REFERENCE  (J,NIM/B,529,68,2022)
FACILITY   (LINAC,3KORPUE) Pohang Accelerator Laboratory (PAL)
INC-SOURCE (BRST) Pulsed electron beam on 0.1 mm thick tungsten
            target
SAMPLE     Natural Cd foil (purity: >99.99%, size: 1.0 cm x 1.0
            cm, weight: 475.6, 496.6 mg)
METHOD     (ACTIV) irradiated for 35 (70 MeV) and 23 min (75 MeV)
           (GSPEC) Started after the cooling time (53-78 hour)
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Energy resolution of 1.8 keV FWHM at 1332.5 keV
            peak of 60Co and detection efficiency of 20% at 1332.5
            keV relative to 3 inch diameter x 3 inch length
            NaI(Tl) detector
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) Total uncertainty                 (4.15-10.64%)
           (ERR-S,2.,10.) Statistical uncertainty          (2-10%)
           (ERR-1) irradiation and cooling time            (~0.5%)
           (ERR-2) detection efficiency                      (~3%)
           (ERR-3) half-life of products, gamma-ray intensity(~2%)
STATUS     (APRVD) Approved by G.N.Kim (2026-01-14)
HISTORY    (20251217C) S.C.Yang
ENDBIB              23
COMMON               3          3
ERR-1      ERR-2      ERR-3
PER-CENT   PER-CENT   PER-CENT
0.5        3.         2.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           30
